Lab1:
    1) You should know the basic commands

#How to create  a directory

mkdir testing

# How to go inside the directory

cd testing

#Create a empty file

touch readme
#See contents of file

cat readme

#List all file

ls 

ls -ltr

ls -la

# How to come out from directory

cd ..

#Help page of any command
man cat
man ls
man mkdir
